            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>et Iunoni <lb n="3"/>Reginae <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audius</ex></expan> Anice<lb break="no" n="5"/>tus <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustalis</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>colon</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Sar</abbr><ex>mizegetusae</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>templum <lb n="8"/>vetustate <lb n="9"/>conlapsum <lb n="10"/>a solo restituit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: nicht vor Commodus, unter dem Apulum zur colonia erhoben wurde; nicht vor Severus Alexander, falls sich coloniar(um) auch auf Sarmizegetusa bezieht.</p>
            </div>
